-- China Sinoma International's First-Half Profit May Increase More Than 50%
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-07T23:59:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-07/china-sinoma-international-s-first-half-profit-may-increase-more-than-50-.html

          
          
             China Sinoma International
Engineering Co.’s first-half net income may increase more than
50 percent from a year earlier after the company increased cost
controls, according to a statement to Shanghai’s stock exchange.  
